abstract: NFL Roundup; Arizona Cardinals defeat Cincinnati Bengals, 34-31; other football scores and news noted.
lead_paragraph: Dallas Cowboys won for the first time since Romo was hurt in Week 2, beating the host Miami Dolphins, 24-14.
